  "repo_truth": "Fresh read-only review of the exact complete HCM-2.2 fourteen-times-remediated planning subject. It freezes future implementation contracts but contains no product implementation, grants no implementation authority before clean closeout, and carries no clean-review conclusion.",
  "allowed_scope": [
    "Remain read-only and replay the sorted complete manifest and aggregate fingerprint before review.",
    "Review every subject byte: 00, 04, 06, fourteen immutable prior dispatches, SPEC, all exact contract/schema/vector/JCS/transcript/API/security/waiver/status/final-use fixtures, plan, unchecked todo, planning proof, and fourteen remediation records.",
    "Read unchanged 01, 02, 03, 05, 07, 08, HCM-0.6 decision, selected HCM-2.1 record/packet/proof, exact live definition assets, and engine/compiler/flow/CLI/skill/template/test sources only as needed.",
    "Run bounded read-only exact schema/JCS/fingerprint/profile/intake, runtime cross-record, raw CTAP2 status/CBOR/authenticator-data/descriptor/DER/ES256, deterministic credential selection, bootstrap ownership, security bound, waiver order, final-use lockout, cross-family recovery, admin DTO, transaction, Markdown/link, Git, handoff, bridge, and classification checks.",
    "Return findings first with exact file/line evidence through the built-in channel."
  ],
  "non_goals": [
